Hive is sql like language over hdfs data leveraging mapReduce via an intermediate xml styled instruction template . 
Hive code converts to a set  of mapReduce steps writtten in xml ( somewhat like oozie ) which triggers MR codes . 

order by is all data reduced in a single reducer , chocking chances 
distribute by is data getting distributed in separate reducers
distirbuted by and sort by is data getting sorted in separate reducers
clustered by is distributed by , sort by both 
